data.Name: Run Tubular
data.Description: DEPRECATED: Please use Code="TubularAssemblyActivityType:RunTubular" with Name="Run Tubular" instead. Pick up casing/liner joints, make it up to a string and run in hole. Includes casing, liner, tie back string, centre pillar and production tubing Does not include drillstring or coiled tubing.

data.Name: Pull Tubular
data.Description: DEPRECATED: Please use Code="TubularAssemblyActivityType:PullTubular" with Name="Pull Tubular" instead. Pull tubular (casing, liner, production tubing or tie back string) out of hole and lay down joints. A tubular normally includes drillstring, but drillstring is not included in this activity, nor coiled tubing.
